                                     MGS
                            for Kids and Teachers

   This page is designed to bring Mars and the Mars Global Surveyor down
   to Earth (no pun intended) for both kids and teachers. Everything is
   readable, non-technical, and most of all FUN -- so enjoy yourself and
   do not be startled if you catch yourself learning, too.

